Odaily Planet Daily News According to the official announcement, Binance Financial Management, One-Click Coin Purchase, Flash Exchange, Leverage, and Contracts will be launched on WalletConnect (WCT). Among them: 
Coin Security Warehouse and Position-by-Position Leverage will add WCT borrowable assets at 19:20 (Eastern Time Zone 8) on April 15, 2025, as well as WCT/USDT, WCT/USDC full position and position-by-position leverage trading pairs; 
Binance will launch WCT 1-75 times U-based perpetual contracts at 19:00 (Eastern Time Zone 8) on April 15, 2025, supporting 75 times leverage.
